casebody.data:
P. Victor GONZALEZ, petitioner,
v.
PLANNED PARENTHOOD OF LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA, et al. No. 14-1080. Supreme Court of the United States May 18, 2015.

Opinion

Motion of Professor Joel D. Hesch for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
